## <a href="#announcements" name="announcements">Announcements</a>

Announcements are general news about the system. They are shown in the `/agent` interface until dismissed. Dismissing an announcement should [mark it as read](#post_announcements_id_mark_as_read).

### <a href="#get_announcements" name="get_announcements">GET /announcements</a>

<%= response(
  announcements: [resource(:announcement)]
) %>

<h3><a href="#post_announcements_id_mark_as_read" name="post_announcements_id_mark_as_read">POST /announcements/:id/mark_as_read</a></h3>

<%= parameters(
  id: '**Required:** ID of the announcement'
) %>

<%= response(
  announcement: resource(:announcement)
) %>

## <a href="#calls" name="calls">Calls</a>

Oh Calls, where do we begin?

